  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "chapterTitle": "《失乐园》：所失何乐，所得何乐",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "926679_18_1747-1912",
          "range": "1747-1912",
          "rangeStart": 1747,
          "rangeEnd": 1912,
          "markText": "人之所以为人，情愿也罢不情愿也罢，都必须受制于责任、义务、伦理道德以至法律、体制、意识形态等种种样样的约束。任何社会留给个人“任性”的空间都是有限的。尤其在男女关系这个敏感地带，任何试图颠覆公认的社会规范和世俗价值观而一味追求本真生命存在状态的努力，都注定以悲剧告终。勇气固然可嘉，但行为不可取。这或许也可称为人之所以为人的宿命。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1720065348,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-04 11:55:48",
          "chapterUid": 18,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1747&rangeEnd=1912",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1747&rangeEnd=1912"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_19_4420-4503",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "4420-4503",
      "markText": "往下别那么孜孜以求了，自由自在地活下去好了！再怎么拼死拼活，一生也还是一生。换个角度看，迄今视为宝贵的东西不那么宝贵了。相反，过去没太看重的东西仿佛陡然变得宝贵起来。",
      "totalCount": 5025,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=4420&rangeEnd=4503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=4420&rangeEnd=4503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_20_4150-4167",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "4150-4167",
      "markText": "休闲这东西，还是忙里偷闲才有意思。",
      "totalCount": 3792,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4150&rangeEnd=4167",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=4150&rangeEnd=4167"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_26_13032-13088",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "13032-13088",
      "markText": "万物皆有一表一里。庄严里面潜伏的淫荡，静谧之中隐秘的痴态，道德背后栖息的背叛——这才是人生至高无上的恬适与快乐。",
      "totalCount": 3133,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=13032&rangeEnd=13088",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=13032&rangeEnd=13088"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_19_5601-5633",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "5601-5633",
      "markText": "每当想到同凛子的相见，久木无不感到恋情的不可思议或恋情的宿命性。",
      "totalCount": 2516,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5601&rangeEnd=5633",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5601&rangeEnd=5633"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_20_7014-7103",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "7014-7103",
      "markText": "“男人所以辛辛苦苦干个没完，归根结底还不是为了抓个好女人据为己有！这是自然界的通理。雄性拼命觅食，打倒对手，最后要得到的无非是雌性的身子和爱情。你死我活争斗不止，就是渴望这个。”",
      "totalCount": 2288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=7014&rangeEnd=7103",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=7014&rangeEnd=7103"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_28_20892-20959",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "20892-20959",
      "markText": "人，只要改变一下价值观，就怎么都能活下去——多少换个看法，迄今看重的东西就已似乎不再有那么重要，而原来认为无所谓的东西就变得宝贵起来。",
      "totalCount": 2211,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=20892&rangeEnd=20959",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=20892&rangeEnd=20959"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_25_15724-15808",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "15724-15808",
      "markText": "人的一生，纵使看上去波澜壮阔，而若从终点回头看，或者意外平庸亦未可知。在这个意义上，无论怎么活都可能留下懊悔。话虽这么说，但还是不想在临终之际哀叹失败或后悔该做的没做。",
      "totalCount": 2184,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=15724&rangeEnd=15808",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=15724&rangeEnd=15808"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_21_15554-15598",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "15554-15598",
      "markText": "中规中矩谨小慎微的女人放荡起来才让人动心。而若一开始就放荡的女人哪怕再放荡，也了无情趣。",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=15554&rangeEnd=15598",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=15554&rangeEnd=15598"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_20_5860-5889",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "5860-5889",
      "markText": "鱼有情水有心，男女之恋这东西，若不是相互吸引是很难成立的。",
      "totalCount": 1935,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5889",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5889"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_19_24141-24215",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "24141-24215",
      "markText": "常识和伦理之类，由于时代的推移，迟早会发生变化。相爱之人的结合乃是普遍的绝对大义。为了守护这宝贵的大义无需畏首畏尾——久木这样说服自己，并深以为然。",
      "totalCount": 1920,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=24141&rangeEnd=24215",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=24141&rangeEnd=24215"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_31_4114-4139",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "4114-4139",
      "markText": "请原谅我们的任性，请把两人葬在一起！只此一个心愿。",
      "totalCount": 1818,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=4114&rangeEnd=4139",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=4114&rangeEnd=4139"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_24_6685-6758",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "6685-6758",
      "markText": "不错，眼下是同妻子处于冷战状态，但直到半年前还是世间普普通通的夫妻。再往前推，还曾是相当要好的夫妻。倘上溯至当初，那可是因为自由恋爱而结婚的一对。",
      "totalCount": 1734,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6685&rangeEnd=6758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=6685&rangeEnd=6758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_27_18703-18758",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "18703-18758",
      "markText": "或许，在婚后埋头于日常这一漩涡中的一瞬间，任何爱都要流于惰性而不断消失。即使同凛子如此刻骨铭心的爱也概莫能外。",
      "totalCount": 1728,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=18703&rangeEnd=18758",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=18703&rangeEnd=18758"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_21_2478-2527",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2478-2527",
      "markText": "朝夕相处这么长时间，与其说是妻子，莫如说是近亲更合适。从实际感受来说，是不可以同近亲发生性关系的。",
      "totalCount": 1683,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2478&rangeEnd=2527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2478&rangeEnd=2527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_25_10717-10761",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "10717-10761",
      "markText": "对离婚那一状态原本是那般渴望，而一旦可以自由了，却又马上不知所措犹豫不决。这是为什么呢？",
      "totalCount": 1494,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=10717&rangeEnd=10761",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=10717&rangeEnd=10761"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_25_12224-12262",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "12224-12262",
      "markText": "妻子究竟有没有类似留恋的心情呢？看这样子，岂不成了冰一样毫无温情可言的女人？",
      "totalCount": 1440,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=12224&rangeEnd=12262",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=12224&rangeEnd=12262"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_27_15293-15340",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "15293-15340",
      "markText": "一切有生命之物，从降生这个世界开始就像原罪一样被身体深处隐藏的本能冲动纠缠不放，为之痛苦挣扎。",
      "totalCount": 1392,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=15293&rangeEnd=15340",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=15293&rangeEnd=15340"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_19_18940-19015",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "18940-19015",
      "markText": "语言终究是诉说不尽的。越用嘴巴说越语无伦次，越莫名其妙。每当如此走投无路之时，就只能用身体相互诉说。烽火四起，短兵相接，偃旗息鼓——于是一切迎刃而解。",
      "totalCount": 1300,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=926679&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=18940&rangeEnd=19015",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/e33326c05e23d7e3362048b?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=18940&rangeEnd=19015"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "926679_21_37291-37305",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "37291-37305",
